Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天 召集大家來不為別的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是希望大家能同舟共濟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}共同克服櫻花莊目前最嚴峻的事態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本次的櫻花莊會議
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}議題是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}關於這位椎名真白同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今早先是幫她穿襪子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}自己把襪子穿上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幫她梳理頭髮時就已經遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}這裡是天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}對我來說是地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 椎名 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}在送她去學校的路上迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好不容易到了學校 卻已經是第二節課了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}快點 跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名有點「特殊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}並不具備常人自力更生的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們應該構築一個大家輪流照顧她的系統...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我經常在想 筆記本電腦和沒穿內褲很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs30\3c&H0000FF&\pos(798.476,650)}ノーパソ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs30\3c&H0000FF&\pos(537.714,650)}ノーパン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 她父母也只說了需要人來照顧她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才決定讓她住進櫻花莊裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}照顧？那老師你就負起責任照顧她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 吃的滿嘴都是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可是為你而開的會議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 這裡沾上了...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}果然很適合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是 就是～！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 那麼真白的保母就決定是神田了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}決定了 決定了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？真白的保母？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 龍他也說贊成哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:11.21,Title,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fs35\c&H92EA9D&\pos(339.428,423.857)}[龍之介大人下線了。]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:11.21,Title,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fs32\c&HAAA6AD&\pos(622.857,182.714)}我可沒閒到有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:11.21,Title,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fs35\c&HAAA6AD&\pos(724.572,326.714)}花費在世俗中無謂的會談上。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}眾望所歸呢 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}散會！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}好了 今晚還要去下護士小姐紀子那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？！這話我可不能當作沒聽到 絕對不能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦...哦 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:35.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord0\shad0\c&HAC9FA6&\frz359.3\pos(515.428,413.571)}真白的保姆就決定是神田空太了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:35.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord0\shad0\c&HAC9FA6&\frz359.3\pos(397.715,447.857)}加油吧學弟！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:35.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord0\shad0\c&HAC9FA6&\frz359.3\pos(412.572,485.572)}我會支持你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 這也太奇怪了吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.72,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}一回目　まぐれで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.72,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}第一次邂逅 若是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.06,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}二回目ってどうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.06,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}那麼第二次 又是如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:07.77,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}偶然じゃないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:07.77,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}果然並非偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:11.48,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}三回 目が合うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:11.48,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}第三次 彼此注視之時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.90,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}変わった人だと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.90,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}真是個怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:18.40,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}割とみんな言うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:18.40,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}大家意外的異口同聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:21.82,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}気になったことは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:21.82,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}但這就是我在意他的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:25.62,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}違うんだ そこじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:25.62,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}不對啦 才不是那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:29.62,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}君は多分　純粋で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:29.62,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}你恐怕十分的純粹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.21,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}純粋を曲げず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.21,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}不願扭曲自身的純粹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:39.51,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}だから小さな日常にさえ立ち向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:39.51,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}所以就連瑣碎的日常 你也依然毫不退步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:43.35,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}夢を持ってきた言葉じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:43.35,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}那些帶來夢想的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.68,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}足りない夢の在り処
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.68,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}描繪夢想缺失的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:50.02,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}きっとこんな風に始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:50.02,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}一定就像是這樣開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.56,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}新しいトキメキ世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.56,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}嶄新而又精彩的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:57.11,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}夢を持ってきた言葉を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:57.11,NCOP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}就把那些帶來夢想的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.82,NCOP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)\blur4}知らない振りしてゆこう
